T(11.5)
\end{array}\right],\left[\begin{array}{c}
M(12.5)\\
T(12.5)
\end{array}\right],\ldots=\\
\left[\begin{array}{c}
261\\
73.941
\end{array}\right],\left[\begin{array}{c}
282\\
79.010
\end{array}\right],\left[\begin{array}{c}
303\\
